<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 09:11:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国卫星发射后台湾发出警报</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-says-chinese-satellite-flies-over-south-taiwan-airspace-2024-01-09/</link><description>台湾当局周二向全岛范围发出警报，称一颗中国卫星飞越台湾南部领空，大约在同一时间，中国官方媒体证实发射了一颗科学卫星。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:50:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-alert-says-chinese-satellite-flies-over-south-taiwan-airspace-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>桥梁困境凸显台湾选举中对中国的分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bridge-dilemma-captures-divide-over-china-taiwan-elections-2024-01-09/</link><description>陈沧江指着办公室一水之隔的厦门摩天大楼，回忆起30年前这座中国南方城市和台湾金门岛一样低矮的情况。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 07:18:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/bridge-dilemma-captures-divide-over-china-taiwan-elections-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>印尼准备与各国合作敲定南海法规</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-ready-work-with-countries-finalise-south-china-sea-code-2024-01-09/</link><description>印度尼西亚外交部长蕾特诺·马尔苏迪周二表示，印度尼西亚准备与其他东南亚国家合作，敲定拖延已久的南海行为准则，该国许多邻国与中国在南海存在重叠的主权声索。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 06:55:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-ready-work-with-countries-finalise-south-china-sea-code-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>经济疲软、新冠疫情肆虐可能导致2023年中国人口再次减少</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/weak-economy-covid-rampage-likely-shrank-chinas-population-again-2023-2024-01-09/</link><description>由于中国突然结束严格的封锁，与新冠病毒相关的死亡人数激增，2023年中国人口可能连续第二年下降，而对经济前景的信心疲弱导致出生率低迷。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 06:03:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/weak-economy-covid-rampage-likely-shrank-chinas-population-again-2023-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着印度关系恶化，马尔代夫总统吸引中国投资者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-president-courts-investors-china-ties-with-india-sag-2024-01-09/</link><description>在中国南部港口城市举行的“投资马尔代夫”论坛上，马尔代夫总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖与面带微笑的当地官员握手并交谈，此次中国之行旨在深化双边关系，因为这个群岛国家正在远离印度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 05:52:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/maldives-president-courts-investors-china-ties-with-india-sag-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪将于下周在印度尼西亚推出汽车 - 公司</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launch-cars-indonesia-next-week-company-2024-01-09/</link><description>中国比亚迪公司周二表示，全球最大的纯电动汽车 (BEV) 销售商将于下周在印度尼西亚推出其汽车。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 05:28:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-giant-byd-launch-cars-indonesia-next-week-company-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>香港领导人表示国泰航空需要解决运力问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-needs-address-capacity-issues-hong-kong-leader-says-2024-01-09/</link><description>香港领导人表示，香港国泰航空计划在繁忙的农历新年期间削减航班，这表明该航空公司需要解决运力问题，而其飞行员工会则呼吁政府进行调查。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 04:22:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-needs-address-capacity-issues-hong-kong-leader-says-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 所有者字节跳动正在与腾讯等公司洽谈出售游戏资产</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tiktok-owner-bytedance-talks-with-tencent-others-sell-gaming-assets-2024-01-09/</link><description>TikTok 母公司字节跳动周二表示，随着这家中国社交媒体公司退出游戏行业，该公司正在与其游戏资产的多个潜在买家进行谈判，其中包括全球最大的视频游戏公司腾讯。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 02:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tiktok-owner-bytedance-talks-with-tencent-others-sell-gaming-assets-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>台湾执政党候选人将维持现状与中国接触</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ruling-party-candidate-will-maintain-status-quo-engage-with-china-2024-01-09/</link><description>台湾执政党总统候选人赖清德周二表示，如果当选，他将维持现状并通过实力追求和平，并在平等和尊严的前提下对与北京接触保持开放态度。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 01:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-ruling-party-candidate-will-maintain-status-quo-engage-with-china-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>台湾国防部称在台湾海峡上空看到四个中国气球</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defence-ministry-says-it-saw-four-chinese-balloons-over-taiwan-strait-2024-01-09/</link><description>台湾国防部周二表示，周一在台湾海峡上空发现了四个中国气球，其中两个气球飞越了台湾岛。</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jan 2024 01:11:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-defence-ministry-says-it-saw-four-chinese-balloons-over-taiwan-strait-2024-01-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国海军水手因与中国分享军事数据被判入狱27个月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-navy-sailor-given-27-months-jail-sharing-military-data-with-china-2024-01-08/</link><description>周一，一名美国海军水手因收受一名中国情报官员近 15,000 美元的贿赂以换取美国非机密私人军事信息的照片而被判处 27 个月监禁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 22:03:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-navy-sailor-given-27-months-jail-sharing-military-data-with-china-2024-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达扩大在中国电动汽车领域的影响力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-expands-its-reach-chinas-ev-sector-2024-01-08/</link><description>英伟达表示，四个中国电动汽车品牌将使用其技术作为自动驾驶系统的大脑，这突显了这家美国芯片制造商尽管华盛顿实施更严格的出口规定，仍决心在中国扩张。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 16:44:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-expands-its-reach-chinas-ev-sector-2024-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>法国干邑白兰地生产商反击中国反倾销调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/french-cognac-makers-hit-back-chinese-anti-dumping-probe-2024-01-08/</link><description>法国干邑白兰地生产商对中国有关他们在中国市场倾销白兰地的说法进行了反击，称所称的价格折扣对于此类正式调查而言异常小。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/french-cognac-makers-hit-back-chinese-anti-dumping-probe-2024-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国堵住地方政府离岸融资漏洞——消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-lgfvs-stop-issuing-offshore-364-day-bonds-sources-2024-01-08/</link><description>四位知情人士告诉路透社，中国监管机构去年堵住了一个监管漏洞，该漏洞允许负债累累的地方政府融资平台（LGFV）进一步增加借款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:12:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-tells-lgfvs-stop-issuing-offshore-364-day-bonds-sources-2024-01-08/</guid></item><item><title>STATBOX 足球-亚洲杯 C 组 - 伊朗、阿联酋、巴勒斯坦、香港</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/statbox-soccer-asian-cup-group-c-iran-uae-palestine-hong-kong-2024-01-08/</link><description>亚洲杯 C 组 Statbox 将于 1 月 12 日至 2 月 10 日在卡塔尔举行：</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jan 2024 10:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/statbox-soccer-asian-cup-group-c-iran-uae-palestine-hong-kong-2024-01-08/</guid></item></channel></rss>